Results for sensitivity, specificity, accuracy, number of misclassified transudate and exudate for TPp, TPr, TNCCp, LDHp, LDHr, Light's criteria (used in parallel with an ‘or’ rule), CHOLp, CHOLr and CHOLg calculated for each of the above parameters using cut-off values obtained by ROC curve analysis of our data (Fig. 1
